#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.sign.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.sign"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:1 of
msgid "Returns an element-wise indication of the sign of a number."
msgstr "返回一个数字符号的逐元素指示。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:3 of
msgid ""
"The `sign` function returns ``-1 if x < 0, 0 if x==0, 1 if x > 0``.  nan "
"is returned for nan inputs."
msgstr ""
"`sign` 函数返回 ``-1 if x < 0, 0 if x==0, 1 if x > 0``。如果输入为 nan，"
"则返回 nan。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:6 of
msgid ""
"For complex inputs, the `sign` function returns ``sign(x.real) + 0j if "
"x.real != 0 else sign(x.imag) + 0j``."
msgstr ""
"对于复数输入，`sign` 函数返回 ``sign(x.real) + 0j if x.real != 0 else "
"sign(x.imag) + 0j``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:9 of
msgid "complex(nan, 0) is returned for complex nan inputs."
msgstr "对于复数 nan 输入，返回 complex(nan, 0)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:11 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:13 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须与输入广播兼容。如果未"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的"
"长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:18 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:23 of
msgid "**y** -- The sign of `x`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 的符号。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sign.sign:28 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"There is more than one definition of sign in common use for complex "
"numbers.  The definition used here is equivalent to :math:`x/\\sqrt{x*x}`"
" which is different from a common alternative, :math:`x/|x|`."
msgstr ""
"对于复数，符号有多种常见定义。这里使用的定义等价于 :math:`x/\\sqrt{x*x}`"
"，它与常见的替代定义 :math:`x/|x|` 不同。"

